    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and will require significant mechanical attention to be roadworthy. The engine suffers from a persistent knock and heavy oil consumption, while the transmission exhibits frequent slipping in higher gears. Cosmetically, the body shows extensive rust on the rocker panels and the interior upholstery is heavily worn and torn. This is a project car best suited for someone with mechanical expertise or for use as a parts donor.",
