    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being offered in poor condition and is recommended only for experienced mechanics or those seeking a dedicated project car. The body shows extensive rust, significant paint fading, and several noticeable dents. Mechanically, the engine requires a complete overhaul, and the transmission is currently slipping; it will likely need to be towed from the lot. The interior has sustained heavy wear, including torn upholstery and non-functional electronics. While it is not currently roadworthy, it could serve as an excellent donor for parts or a complete restoration project for the right enthusiast.",
